name: .DML File Extension
summary: Learn about .DML files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Web script written in DynaScript, a specialized Dynamic HTML scripting language; contains code that can be used to dynamically generate HTML; may be executed on any Web server that has DynaScript installed.

content: DML pages are similar to ColdFusion (.CFM) and Active Server (.ASP) pages. The DynaScript language uses a C-oriented syntax and supports "Intelligent Objects," which can help reduce the development time of Web applications.
